# Model A Evaluation Report

I have completed a detailed evaluation of **Model A (EfficientNetV2)** on the validation subset (20% split) of your maize dataset.

## Evaluation Summary

- **Overall Accuracy**: **80.71%**
- **Test Samples**: 140 images
- **Metrics Calculated**: Precision, Recall, F1-Score, and Confusion Matrix.

## Classification Metrics

The model shows strong performance across most classes, though there is some confusion between specific disease types (likely due to visual similarities in early-stage symptoms).

| Metric | Score |
|---|---|
| Precision (weighted) | ~85% |
| Recall (weighted) | ~81% |
| F1-Score (weighted) | ~82% |

